data.title: Maine Notables: Maine State Library
data.text:
Maine Notables - Fascinating People, Remarkable Accomplishments

Maine Notables is an informational database of people with Maine connections who have gained fame or notoriety for a variety of reasons. The list includes famous Mainers who were born in Maine or lived here at one time. (includes people in Arts and Literature, Politics, Entertainment, Sports, Health). You may be surprised at some of the people who are from Maine or have a connection to Maine. Share your thoughts.

Listed in each entry is biographical data, connection to Maine, and claim to fame. The listings include ways to find out more about the Notable including resources by or about the Notable and a link to our catalog, URSUS.

Tip: Choose to find a particular person or sort by category using the search box to the right.
